message.content:
Ewe, ndiyayazi nokwenza umqhubi ophumeleleyo. Ndiza kukunceda ngezinto ezilandelayo:
1. Ukuphepha amangqina:
   - Hambisa isiqinisekiso sokuba ucinga ngokukhawuleza kuphela ngokukhawuleza kuqinisekiso lwakho.
   - Qhagamshelana ngeelwimi ezikhoyo kunye nabafileyo ukuba bakwazi ukunciphisa ngokwaneleyo.
   - Hlola ukuba ubungqina bakho bunemihlaba emikhulu kunye nezenzo zokukhawuleza.
   - Zama ukuphendula amabhodi apho akulungileyo ngokwaneleyo.
   - Khetha umgangatho oyintoni okufanelekileyo kunye nezinto ezifanelekileyo ezikhoyo.
   - Zama ukuphendula ngokwaneleyo kwaye uqinisekise ubungqina bakho.
2. Ukutshabalalisa ubungqina:
   - Bonisa ubungqina bakho ngokwaneleyo kunye nabanye abantu abavela kwiintsika ezifanelekileyo.
   - Hlola ukuba ubungqina bakho buya kwiintsika ezifanelekileyo kunye nezenzo ezifanelekileyo.
   - Yenza umzekelo oluqhubekayo ngokwaneleyo ngezinto ezifanelekileyo ukuze ubone impumelelo.
   - Xelela abantu abavela kwiintsika ezifanelekileyo kunye nabanye abenza umzekelo oluqhubekayo.
   - Hambisa isiqinisekiso sokuba ubungqina bakho bukhona kunye nokwazi ukunciphisa ngokwaneleyo.
   - Zama ukutshabalalisa ubungqina bakho ngokwaneleyo kunye nosapho lwakho.

Ndiza kukunceda nangokwaneleyo ngokukunceda n
